(843, '杨先生', '13607360670', '', 0, 0, 0, '常德市武陵区三岔路外临江路', '{"room":"4","hall":"2","bathroom":"2"}', 4, 2, 2, 162.00, 55.00, '{"floor":"6","total_floor":"6"}', 6, 6, '', 0, 0, '', '[]', '创鼎百合园毛坯房出售', '', '<p style="border: 0px; font-family: Arial, simsun, sans-serif, 宋体; font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; line-height: 2; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="border: 0px; font-size: 9pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">1</span><span style="border: 0px; font-size: 9pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">、升值空间大：沅江三桥于<span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">2013</span>年<span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">7</span>月通车，芙蓉南路不久就会与沅安路拉通,界时创鼎百和园肯定随着交通便利升值。而且该房正处在常德智慧谷(常德教育文化产业园)附近,近年将有几所大专院校和文化中心迁至此处(如常德幼师学院、常德技师学院、常德财经职业学院和文化产业单位等)，大量的教职员工会在附近买房，因此，此处房产肯定会热闹起来。</span><br /></p><p style="border: 0px; font-family: Arial, simsun, sans-serif, 宋体; font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; line-height: 2; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="border: 0px; font-size: 9pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">2</span>、交通方便：<span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">29</span>路、<span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">30</span>路公交车从创鼎百和园门前过。向东北方向走<span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">700</span>米，可到达三岔路口，这里有通向火车站、东门、德山，桥南、桃源等地的公交车。</span><br /></p><p style="border: 0px; font-family: Arial, simsun, sans-serif, 宋体; font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; line-height: 2; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="border: 0px; font-size: 9pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">3</span>、是住家的好地方：距屈原公园<span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">200</span>米，距沅江<span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">500</span>米，空气新鲜，锻炼身体有去处。</span><br /></p><p style="border: 0px; font-family: Arial, simsun, sans-serif, 宋体; font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; line-height: 2; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="border: 0px; font-size: 9pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">4</span>、距繁华地段近，走公园内，只走不到十分钟，可以到达全市最大的超市梅尼广场、汽车北站和九重天大酒店。走沅安路开车（不会出现堵车现象）只要10分钟就会到达下南门繁华区。</span><br /></p><p style="border: 0px; font-family: Arial, simsun, sans-serif, 宋体; font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm